name: Gift of Gatherer of the Hunt
description:
Combine a Gift of Gatherer of the Hunt, a Gift of Uncovered Grounds, a Gift of Expertise, and a Bloodstone Shard in the Mystic Forge to create the Gift of Janthir Wilds.

Created in the Mystic Forge by combining:
• 100 Sweet-Treated Pine Planks
• 100 Neutralized Titan Alloys
• 100 Shards of Lowland Shore
• 100 Shards of Janthir Syntri
